							<code code="DI12" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.17.243"/>
							<title>IVU Report</title>
							<text>The control film shows a 5mm calcified opacity to the left of the transverse process of L2 in the line of the left ureter. Following injection of contrast there was prompt excretion on the right. On the left there is a persistant dense nephrogram. There is no excretion on the left at 45 mins. The patient was transferred to ultrasound. See ultrasound report.</text>
						</section>
